{"tid":781347,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市全滅!【大師點睇】騰訊短線跌過龍 沈大師：跌到$320 我一定加Call！","createTime":"2018-08-15T23:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T01:25:25.000Z","uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1589828da0ce8ab98756e6fcd6470271d9c3f7","tid":781347,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58568276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58568276&d=nkxv9pFi4VjXiou7Gv4Lbf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=54ddb505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58568276&h=32850e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58568276</a><br />\n<br />\n【大師點睇】騰訊短線跌過龍 沈大師：跌到$320 我一定<span style=\"color: red;\">加Call</span>！<br />\n<br />\n沈大師發威！騰訊（700）今日公佈業績，差於市場預期，訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈表示，短線會<span style=\"color: red;\">博反彈</span>，如果明日見320元會Call，但料<span style=\"color: red;\">今年底見300元</span>。<br />\n沈大師指，「其實業績係差，但<span style=\"color: red;\">意料之內</span>，唔係真係想像中差到咁離譜。」騰訊第二季，按非通用會計準則（Non-GAAP），季度純利197.16億元，按年升20%，<span style=\"color: red;\">勝預期</span>。<br />\n他表示，網絡遊戲業務，第二季收入為252.02億元，環比跌12%，但同比錄升6%，「呢條數咁係合理架，因為通常第二季係會差啲，呢個亦都係預期。」他提到，現時網絡遊戲收入，比上年第二及第四季好，但差於去年第三季，「但第三季係旺季，所以唔係差得咁緊要。即係差就一定係差，但唔係心裡面諗到咁差。」<br />\n今日騰訊股價再下挫，最低見335元，全日收跌3.6%報336元。大師認為，「<span style=\"color: red;\">梗係Over-react</span>。依家外圍跌到320蚊，我梗係加佢Call啦！<span style=\"color: red;\">唔使諗。呢啲位冇得沽啦，仲點沽呀。</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他指出，自己年初已預期騰訊會跌至320元，現時亦已到目標價。他再一次強調，預期騰訊要到年底才見300元，但短線會反彈，「我一路都講短期320蚊我一家買架！去到出第三季業績，就見真章啦。」策略方面，現時會Call騰訊，當騰訊彈上370元至380元水平，就食糊。<br />\n至於彭博引述消息人士指出，內地監管機構凍結了網絡遊戲版號審批，消息令行業出現混亂，這主要由於中央關注網絡遊戲出現暴力及賭博成份所致。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大師表示，「彭博冇次準架！全部流架！以前就大半半，依家『彭博引述消息人士』嗰啲呢，七成係流嘅，次次最後都冇發生，跟住郁到個市。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edde42813e84cebc93ec612fbb3ef172ff5a73c","tid":781347,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:53:11.000Z","msg":"大師都幾重貨 700"},{"pid":"3b8f1d6b0e97ee0e62be251a11fbd420b2ccf1ad","tid":781347,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"當大師變好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79939aa5e2a0d88dd126414738546d29a4117d36","tid":781347,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"全滅=全升 all in 吧"},{"pid":"d3a3a02758ed10b6c5ecf2443519a4177bb32526","tid":781347,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"大師重手call啊點算啊世界末日啦"},{"pid":"4c490716f1aac80ab1d2e3fd1ce6f3a787fbbca2","tid":781347,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3a3a02758ed10b6c5ecf2443519a4177bb32526","tid":781347,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"大師重手call啊點算啊世界末日啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢講野相反的"},{"pid":"b2c85c51d934bea9296974515e5d6295e8736a48","tid":781347,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:18:23.000Z","msg":"擾敵"},{"pid":"d07c8375fcfb52611fa6151e26fa133cffd12b49","tid":781347,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3edde42813e84cebc93ec612fbb3ef172ff5a73c","tid":781347,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:53:11.000Z","msg":"大師都幾重貨 700"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018